脂肪）啦，咁其實肥婆既科研價值係咪遠遠高於佢既食用價值呢？<br />\n<br />\n如是者，我地應該捉返啲聲稱飲水都會肥既肥婆去實驗室，慢慢研究佢地如何將水變成脂肪。地球有高達八成係水，如果解鎖到〔feypo transformation - H2O to fat〕呢個科技，根本就等於有無限既能源。到時就好似matrix咁，捉拎曬啲肥婆去做energy plant，簡直係人類科技一個最大既里程碑<br />\n<br />\n之後甚至可以研發肥婆彈，肥婆引擎，肥婆反重力裝置。到時人類稱霸宇宙就指日可待<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過如果最後研究證明，肥婆原來飲水係唔會肥，咁到時就可以大大巴車落佢塊肥面度。<br />\n「飲水都會肥呀喇！」<br />\n「偷食肉呀喇！」<br />\n「女神呀喇！」<br />\n佢就唯有死死氣去百佳買美極。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又講得幾好"},{"pid":"0ca9f550a82e5206313a47111bf5a873a3748ab8","tid":326252,"uid":17835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"以貌取人係有<br />\n但十個肥婆有九個都心理變態被迫害妄想症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfaeb12bde2d4e69ec19c4fcd11d3d9bcefbcc58","tid":326252,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以貌取人係有<br />\n但十個肥婆有九個都心理變態被迫害妄想症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己肥又唔減覺得冇問題 人地話佢肥又話人歧視乜乜柒柒 都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aaad8108e1426e6c9af11a29d6ba7beb470a7d2","tid":326252,"uid":59989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:45:20.000Z","msg":"好多靚女都係打份工<br />\n真係高層果啲個樣都幾西<br />\n點解釋"},{"pid":"1587ad524823ac2ad4387fb2d6985131dfc43a79","tid":326252,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>肥=自控能力有問題<br />\n點升你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲水肥個d 呢❔</blockquote><br />\n呼吸肥個d 呢 ?"},{"pid":"9e11fa8eaf473569ab19e14df713c